des: The Lighthouse WECC in Southeast GA and Northeast FL is Shining HIS Light through Contemporary Christian and Praise & Worship Music. Our mission is to encourage your faith walk with music and ministry that will light your path and your day. God bless you and thank you for tuning in on-line!
